.github/
# scripts/ is intentionally included in the image (seed, export tools)
# rust/ is only read by Dockerfile's WITH_RUST=1 build path (and never at
# all by the WITH_RUST=0 default) — target/ is local build output, can
# reach several hundred MB to GB, and must never bloat the build context
# sent to the daemon even when unused.
rust/target/
rust/**/target/

